## ğŸ“Š Comparison

| Feature | OHM MCP | Traditional Tools |
|---------|---------|-------------------|
| Accuracy | 100% AST | ~70% Regex |
| Safety | Auto backup/rollback | Manual |
| Testing | Auto-generates | Manual |
| Automation | Full | Suggestions only |
